no}}</ref>，同時召回日本駐莫斯科大使以示抗議<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2010/nov/02/japan-recall-ambassador-medvedev-dispute|title=Japan recalls envoy to Russia over Kurils dispute|publisher=The Guardian|date=2010-11-02|accessdate=2010-11-23|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612180927/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2010/nov/02/japan-recall-ambassador-medvedev-dispute|dead-url=no}}</ref>。訪問後隔日，俄羅斯聯邦外交部部長[[謝爾蓋·維克托羅維奇·拉夫羅夫|謝爾蓋·拉夫羅夫]]表示總統梅德維傑夫還計畫多次出訪爭議島嶼<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A13NI20101102 "Russia warns of more visits to disputed islands"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A13NI20101102 |date=20101206082835 }}, Reuters, Nov. 02, 2010</ref>。

